              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15108278129082065082">I love this book, it&apos;s been a while since I re-read it but my God does it pack a punch.<br/><br/>Had me crying on the train!<br/><br/>Definitely a must-read not just for the romance, action, tension and characters but because it will make you think.<br/><br/>I plan to marathon the trilogy now as I have never read the other two books.</span>
  <span id="freeText15108278129082065082" style="display:none">I love this book, it's been a while since I re-read it but my God does it pack a punch.<br /><br />Had me crying on the train!<br /><br />Definitely a must-read not just for the romance, action, tension and characters but because it will make you think.<br /><br />I plan to marathon the trilogy now as I have never read the other two books.</span>
